headline: Prediction: Freeport McMoRan Stock Will Soar Over the Next 10 Years. 1 Reason Why.
summary: If the price of copper doesn't rise or stays within the current range, it won't make sense to buy copper miner Freeport-McMoRan (NYSE: FCX).  The Motley Fool Stock Advisor analyst team just identified what they believe are the 10 best stocks for investors to buy now… and Freeport-McMoRan wasn’t one of them.
